{2040}{}{You got any bounties?}
{2050}{}{I'm here for another bounty.}
{2060}{}{I took care of that bounty for you.}
{2070}{}{Nothing today, thanks.}
{3000}{}{This is the last piece of Chinese history right here! After the Great War, what was left of the Chinese ended up here. We're slowly rebuilding our home, and nothing is going to stop us. Not you, or the NCR.}
{3010}{}{Well alright then.}
{4000}{}{A Communist is a fine outstanding individual! It's also our form of government. We're communists. We believe in equality for all! A better today, tomorrow, and yesterday!}
