{6000}{}{Hell yes. Some bad people out here all over the ruins. They keep attacking the caravans. I've been tracking them down, and marking their locations all over the map. The Communists are willing to pay anyone that can get the job done.}
{6010}{}{Go on. What else can you tell me?}
{7000}{}{Good. Got some mean mother fuckers ready to kill. Are you ready to head out now?}
